name: BLACKLETTER TEE
description:
We're back.


The Blacketter tee is our first release in a year and we're hoping that we won't keep you waiting that long for the next.

The tee has quite a standard fit so if you want a baggier fit go for a size up.

Delivery: 4-7 Days

Printed on American Apparel

Size Guide (Centimetres):

Small - 45 W
Medium - 50 W
Large -  55 W
X-Large - 60 W

(W=Width across chest)

name: HATE CREW TEE
description:
OHC

We fly the banner of hate. We hate loads of aspects of the current independent clothing scene, so instead of releasing some 5-panel or camo jacket, we're releasing the HATE CREW tee. Old school varsity style.

We recommend you buy a size bigger if you prefer a baggier fit, as the tees are quite fitted.

Delivery: 4-7 days

Printed on Gildan Softstyle

Size Guide (Centimetres):

Small - 46 W, 68 L
Medium - 51 W, 70 L
Large - 56 W, 73 L
Extra Large - 61 W, 75 L

(W=Chest Width, L=Length)
